glish_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Sex is zero","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Le film suit l'histoire de Eun-shik, désespérément amoureux d'une fille et qui, malgré beaucoup d'efforts, se retrouve toujours dans des situations toutes plus tordues les unes que les autres. Et ce n'est pas son groupe d'amis, complètement tarés et obsédés qui va arranger cela..."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Sex is zero","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Narra la historia de Eun-shik, un estudiante locamente enamorado de una chica, y que, a pesar de todos sus esfuerzos para estar con ella, se encuentra siempre en situaciones de lo más enrevesadas, todo ello ayudado de su grupo de amigos, a cada cual más loco y pervertido."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Сексът е нищо","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Действието се развива в колеж, където 28-годишният Eun-shik копнее за Eun-hyo - най-популярното момиче. Тя обаче е влюбена в Sangok- плейбоя на колежа. Следват нескопосани и неуспешни опити на Eun-shik да спечели любовта и, но той може само да гледа момичето на мечтите му в обятията на егоистичния Sangok. Междувременно съквартирантите на Eun-shik се опитват да забият приятелките на Eun-hyo."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Sex Is Zero - American Pie war gestern...","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nach Ableistung seines Wehrdienstes beginnt Eun-sik seine Laufbahn als Student an der Universität. Doch dort wird er schnell, aufgrund seines Alters und seiner Begabung immer am falschen Ort zur falschen Zeit zu sein, zu einem Außenseiter. Kein Wunder, dass auch seine Schwärmerei für die schöne Studentin Eun-hyo äußerst fruchtlos verläuft, nicht zuletzt auch, weil sie eh schon in den coolsten Typ auf dem Campus verschossen ist. Freilich hat der Gott der Liebe ein Auge auf die beiden jungen Leute, aber leider auch einen absurden Sinn für Humor. Und so ist der Weg zum gemeinsamen Glück mit diversen Stolpersteinen gepflastert."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Секса круглый ноль","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Юноша влюбляется в девушку, которая определенно другого социального уровня и ему предстоит долгий путь, чтобы заслужить ее любовь."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"색즉시공","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"군대 제대 후 늦깎이 대학생이 된 은식. 남보다 늦은 출발 때문에 고시 합격에 인생 목표를 건다. 하지만 대학에 들어가자마자 해병대 고참 성국을 만나게 되고 그의 꾐에 빠져 차력 동아리에 가입하고 만다. 불철주야 공부를 해도 모자랄 판에 웬 차력? 그런데 거기에 또 하나, 그의 꿈을 가로막는 장애가 있었으니."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"色即是空","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"服完兵役的高龄大学生恩植（任昌丁饰）就读于法律系，校园里满是对性充满好奇的年轻男女。可惜外表憨直的他没有什么女人缘，脑筋也是不大好使。一次偶然机会，恩植认识了学校健身俱乐部的头牌队员、校花级美女银孝（河智苑饰），他立马被对方的美貌性感吸引。恩植想尽办法接进银孝，博取好感，却都以失败告终，甚至引发许多误会，比如在公车上，他被银孝当成色狼一脚踢中要害。后来，银孝迷住了有钱的花花公子相旭（郑敏饰），甚至怀了孕，但最终被抛弃，伤心绝望。与此同时，恩植和银孝之间产关系有了微妙变化。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"סקס זה כלום","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"קומדיית נעורים קוריאנית מטורפת ברוח סרטי \"אמריקן פאי\" ו\"בית החיות\" שזכתה להצלחה במולדתה והפכה לקומדיה הקוריאנית המצליחה ביותר בכל הזמנים. הסרט העוקב אחר צעירים שטופי הורמונים במיטב מסורת ה\"אמריקן פאי\" מערבב בתוכו סקס, נעורים ורומנטיקה ומושפע בעיקר מהומור צעירים אמריקני, בעיקר סרטי \"אמריקן פאי\" ו\"נעורים בקצב מהיר\"."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Сексу круглий нуль","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Юнак закохується в дівчину, яка безумовно іншого соціального рівня і в нього попереду довгий шлях, щоб заслужити її любов."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Sex Is Zero","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"O enredo segue a história do estudante de faculdade Eun-shik Jang e seus esforços para impressionar uma estudante junior Eun-hyo Lee. Eun-Shik tem o hábito de encontrar-se em situações um tanto estranhas, que muitas vezes o constrange e sabota suas tentativas para impressionar Eun-hyo Lee."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Sex Is Zero","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"På Sunjong-universitetet får vi följa en grupp studenter och deras liv tillsammans. Klassisk collegefilm i koreansk tappning."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"色即是空","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"恩植長得粗礦健壯，只可惜的頭腦有點愚笨憨直，他高中畢業後像韓國其他能進入大學的青年一樣，被招入了部隊。等服完兵役之後，才去讀大學，所以，在班級裡，他要比其他同學大三、四歲。恩植就讀的是法律系，他的夢想是順利地通過律師資格考試，成為一名合格的律師。  學期開始後不久，因為恩植曾經服過兵役，怎麼說都練過幾招，加上他孔武有力，被學校的武術社團邀請加入，恩植開始了在學習法律之餘，參加社團的武術活動。  一次偶然的機會，他認識了學校另外一個學生社團有氧舞蹈社的隊員恩俞，立刻被她的性感美貌吸引住了。恩俞是學校的校花，身材火爆，跳起體操，恩植直盯她繃緊的臀部和乳房，口水直流。  恩植暗戀恩俞，在公車上在被誤會是色狼，被恩俞一踢在了要害部位，疼得他倒在車箱裡哇哇大叫。一場誤會讓他們成為好友。甚至有一次，他對著電腦的淫穢畫面手淫時，被恩俞撞見。雖然恩俞跟學校的花心大帥哥交往，恩植依然對她很好甚至下海當「牛郎」賺錢，只為買下恩俞喜歡的戒指，當生日禮物送她。直到恩俞不小心懷孕，恩植仍然陪著她去墮胎，並且在身旁細心的照顧她，最後她終於明白真正喜歡她的人是恩植 . . . . ."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Semmi szex","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A film folytatja az Amerikai Pite által megkezdett tinivígjátékok sorát, amolyan ázsiai módra, csak valamivel poénosabb, és jobban kivitelezett mint előbb említett \"nyugati\" elődje. Könnyed - néhol azért erősen morbid humor, és jól eltalált drámai szál jellemzi. A karakterek kedvelhetőek, a történet egyszerű, de kedvelhető kis film."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Saekjeuk Shigong","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"De 28 jarige nietsnut Eun-hyo, is gek op een meisje bij hem op school en doet er alles voor om haar te krijgen. Helaas zorgt zijn pervers gedrag ervoor dat ze steeds minder in hem gaat zien, totdat hij haar gaat steunen bij een zeer moeilijke situatie."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"我班 Friend 好搞嘢","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"恩植長得粗礦健壯，只可惜的頭腦有點愚笨憨直，他高中畢業後像韓國其他能進入大學的青年一樣，被招入了部隊。等服完兵役之後，才去讀大學，所以，在班級裏，他要比其他同學大三、四歲。恩植就讀的是法律系，他的夢想是順利地通過律師資格考試，成為一名合格的律師。\r 學期開始後不久，因為恩植曾經服過兵役，怎麼説都練過幾招，加上他孔武有力，被學校的武術社團邀請加入，恩植開始了在學習法律之餘，參加社團的武術活動。\r 一次偶然的機會，他認識了學校另外一個學生社團有氧舞蹈社的隊員恩俞，立刻被她的性感美貌吸引住了。恩俞是學校的校花，身材火爆，跳起體操，恩植直盯她繃緊的臀部和乳房，口水直流。\r 恩植暗戀恩俞，在公車上在被誤會是色狼，被恩俞一踢在了要害部位，疼得他倒在車箱裏哇哇大叫。一場誤會讓他們成為好友。甚至有一次，他對著電腦的淫穢畫面手淫時，被恩俞撞見。雖然恩俞跟學校的花心大帥哥交往，恩植依然對她很好甚至下海當「牛郎」賺錢，只為買下恩俞喜歡的戒指，當生日禮物送她。直到恩俞不小心懷孕，恩植仍然陪著她去墮胎，並且在身旁細心的照顧她，最後她終於明白真正喜歡她的人是恩植 . . . . ."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"ปิ๊ด ปี้ ปิ๊ด ยกก๊วน กิ๊กสาว","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"หลังจากปลดประจำการจากกรมทหาร ผนวกกับความใฝ่ฝันที่ะทำงานเป็นผู้พิพากษา อึนซิก ในวัย 28 จึงต้องฝืนสังขาร สมัครเข้าเรียนมหาวิทยาลัย และต้องปลอมตัวลดอายุ เพื่อจะได้เข้ากลุ่มกับเพื่อนวัยละอ่อนได้ไม่ขัดเขิน เขากับเพื่อน จอมทะลึ่งอีก 3 คน เช่าห้องพักในมหาวิทยาลัย กิจวัตรยามว่าง คือ การดูวีซีดีหนังเรดเอ็กซ์ แล้ววิพากษ์วิจารณ์อย่างปากจัดเป็นที่สนุกสนาน"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Sex Is Zero","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Patru băieți, Sangok, Chansu, Songguk și amicul lor roșcat locuiesc în aceeași cameră. Chansu o adoră pe frumoasa Youngzoonk. El este cel mai prostănac dintre cei patru. El se sperie de fum și sare pe geam din cămin, mănâncă pâine care avea otravă pentru șoareci și multe altele... Songguk are o relație de iubire cu Yoomi. Sangok o iubește enorm pe Eunhyo, care însă îl preferă pe Eunsik. Studenții se pregătesc de un concurs pe facultăți, ce va fi televizat. Din acest moment încep încurcăturile amoroase și năzbâtiile, care fac deliciul filmului."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Saekjeuk shigong","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Eun-Sik není ani tak hlupák, jako spíš naivní smolař, který má štěstí leda tak na nepříjemné náhody a nehody. Poté, co absolvoval povinnou vojenskou službu, se mu konečně podařilo nastoupit na místní univerzitu, kde se zabývá studiem práva. A i přesto, že od ostatních studentů má věkem hezkých pár let odstup, rozhodně se o něm nedá říct, že by vedl kdovíjak spořádaný život. Pije a často se probouzí ve vlastních zvratcích, při tanci na diskotéce vypadá jako idiot a ani při sexu dvakrát neboduje a je odkázán pouze na své vlastní představy. Jednoho dne ale konečně potká dívku svého srdce. Je jí Eun-Hyo – krásná mladá žena cvičící ve školním aerobikovém družstvu a členka národního týmu. Na první pohled by se mohlo zdát, že je jejich společná budoucnost pouhým snem, ale Eun-Hyo není povrchní, a tak dá Eun-Sikovi nejednu šanci dobýt její srdce. Jenže Eun-Sik je prostě Eun-Sik a než se naděje, svoji poslední šanci promarní a mezi něj a jeho lásku vstoupí někdo třetí."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Tình Dục Là Chuyện Nhỏ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"セックス・イズ・ゼロ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Sex is Zero","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Narra la historia de Eun-shik, un estudiante locamente enamorado de una chica, y que, a pesar de todos sus esfuerzos por estar con ella, se encuentra siempre en situaciones de lo más embarazosas, siempre ayudado de su grupo de amigos, un grupo de lo más alocado y pervertido."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Seks Hiçbir Şeydir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Eun-shik, askerlik görevinden sonra üniversitede okurken eyalet sınavını geçmeye çalışır. Bir gün güzel bir kadın olan Eun-hyo ile tanışır ve hayatı değişir."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":30112,"adult":false,"title":"Lost in Beijing","video":false,"overview":"A look at modern-day life in China's capital centered on a ménage-a-quatre involving a young woman, her boss, her husband and her boss's wife.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.8946,"vote_count":61,"poster_path":"/2LZ7qbdnCqlOzlngcj5wdvnLfjA.jpg","release_date":"2007-09-26","vote_average":6.541,"backdrop_path":"/7F1djgcBJkMWFOeQ0ZK4b5Q3LPb.jpg","original_title":"苹果","original_language":"zh"},{"id":21647,"adult":false,"title":"Sex Is Zero 2","video":false,"overview":"In his 10th year at college, Eun-sik is part of a nearly ideal campus couple with swimming champ Kyung-ah. While their three-year relationship is solid, Eun-sik struggles to get to the next level with Kyung-ah; despite the help and support of his friends, he can't manage to get her into bed.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6678,"vote_count":67,"poster_path":"/iEymewxcv8YKl5Ry6NIekagx58x.jpg","release_date":"2007-12-12","vote_average":5.612,"backdrop_path":"/1wXvVdS7KV9ylD3sZ8Ure3f1xhm.jpg","original_title":"색즉시공 시즌 2","original_language":"ko"},{"id":338803,"adult":false,"title":"The Treacherous","video":false,"overview":"The story of Joseon's tyrant king Yeonsan who exploits the populace for his own carnal pleasures, his seemingly loyal retainer who controls him and all court dealings, and a woman who seeks vengeance.","genre_ids":[18,36,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.6911,"vote_count":88,"poster_path":"/1YpS9sXZ8bRrmPwULftGbfwImnR.jpg","release_date":"2015-05-21","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/qFq2Ixo3XApoTp1H7JCTgLfGwVk.jpg","original_title":"간신","original_language":"ko"},{"id":15384,"adult":false,"title":"Red Cliff II","video":false,"overview":"The battle of Red Cliff continues and the alliance between Xu and East Wu is fracturing.  With Cao Cao's massive forces on their doorstep, will the kingdoms of Xu and East Wu survive?","genre_ids":[28,12,18,36,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.5547,"vote_count":484,"poster_path":"/h4WZHa5K941lAthsa29g0RFJJtV.jpg","release_date":"2009-01-07","vote_average":7.273,"backdrop_path":"/taC4SMRB4UUbXL9R4680aJ4ejQK.jpg","original_title":"赤壁：決戰天下","original_language":"zh"},{"id":10421,"adult":false,"title":"War of the Buttons","video":false,"overview":"For generations, two rival French villages, Longueverne and Velrans, have been at war. But this is no ordinary conflict, for the on-going hostilities are between two armies of young schoolboys. When he is beaten by his father for having lost his buttons, the leader of the Longueverne army, Lebrac, has an idea which will give his side the advantage: next time, he and his brave soldiers will go in battle without their clothes...","genre_ids":[35,18,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8529,"vote_count":284,"poster_path":"/tg3RwUclgnW3hM1ExHkMd71YQ0n.jpg","release_date":"1962-04-18","vote_average":7.224,"backdrop_path":"/o0vdiPmh1oEpyZ1hSSPnb6tKPRd.jpg","original_title":"La Guerre des boutons","original_language":"fr"},{"id":16632,"adult":false,"title":"100 Days with Mr. Arrogant","video":false,"overview":"After being dumped by her boyfriend just before their 100-day anniversary, Ha-young meets a college guy named Hyung-joon when she kicks a can that accidentally hits him in the face and causes him to scratch his Lexus. He demands she pay him $3000 on the spot.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7746,"vote_count":107,"poster_path":"/4kTS3R0NR7Y5t1OpIuVWURlFYBF.jpg","release_date":"2004-01-16","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/u7brIZ1clOun8Mc5x2Au6NScMxg.jpg","original_title":"내 사랑 싸가지","original_language":"ko"},{"id":40580,"adult":false,"title":"Hello, Schoolgirl","video":false,"overview":"Kwon Yeon-woo is a thirty year old low-level civil servant who works in a district office; quite innocent for his age, he has been on numerous blind dates in an unsuccessful bid to find a wife. After moving into a new place, he begins to encounter a high school girl, Soo-yeong, on his way to work every morning, and she begins to develop feelings for him. Meanwhile, Kang Sook has just started working at the district office straight out of high school, and falls head over heels for older woman Kwon Ha-kyeong.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6626,"vote_count":52,"poster_path":"/tmuG77YQEoXDQu3ypJadgc8FDmJ.jpg","release_date":"2008-11-27","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/3KmpNFjYDB6tS6G5U3JCpsJETFy.jpg","original_title":"순정만화","original_language":"ko"},{"id":45022,"adult":false,"title":"Holy Rollers","video":false,"overview":"Inspired by actual events in the late nineties when Hasidic Jews were recruited as mules to smuggle ecstasy from Europe into the United States.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4981,"vote_count":90,"poster_path":"/594RhDOkzRXkQM30XKjEG0843Ol.jpg","release_date":"2010-05-21","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/rBfsRRpNFxXYt7z5FpNc9t5Cdpe.jpg","original_title":"Holy Rollers","original_language":"en"},{"id":418827,"adult":false,"title":"Sister's Younger Husband","video":false,"overview":"A sexy brother-in-law approached her? And he’s a younger man?  Mi-yeon, who was adopted into her family when she was little, is living with her older sister, Si-yeon and Si-yeon’s husband. Mi-yeon’s desire towards her brother-in-law grows more and more every night when she gets to watch the affectionate interaction between her older sister and the brother-in-law. One day, Mi-yeon seduces her brother-in-law and the two end up crossing the line when they should not have. As the situation goes on, Mi-yeon finds out her older sister is also having affairs outside the marriage. Mi-yeon tries to clear up the relationship with her brother-in-law out of guilty feeling. However, she hears something shocking from the brother-in-law.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4964,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/uIHz015EH7VnqSRCymBKwD7iSiX.jpg","release_date":"2016-10-11","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/2dM48FnfVRAIkO9fkT8ZQLDxRNn.jpg","original_title":"젊은 형부","original_language":"ko"},{"id":784610,"adult":false,"title":"A Way Station","video":false,"overview":"Young lovers, Seung-hyeon and Ji-a, were drifted apart without even getting a chance to open themselves up. 7 years later, they meet again in their hometown. Embracing their feelings for each other at last, they fall in love once again and share cherishable moments together.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.432,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/186r1DnR9hHipdwFigNYlcF1ALL.jpg","release_date":"2021-02-18","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/y12yGohzantqzmT2CGKFFj2KqxX.jpg","original_title":"간이역","original_language":"ko"},{"id":50714,"adult":false,"title":"Reflections","video":false,"overview":"Europol Agent Tom Brindle is called to Barcelona, Spain, to track down the notorious serial killer known as Pygmalion. A set of fingerprints lead to a young, volatile soldier, Marco Soler. Agent Brindle arrests Marco and intensely interrogates him, convinced that he has his man. Marco has an airtight alibi though and further investigation of the suspect leads Agent Brindle to a shocking discovery.","genre_ids":[53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.544,"vote_count":17,"poster_path":"/hDUL9rcoiyqRjUWvqcmS5Fb6fOr.jpg","release_date":"2008-06-24","vote_average":4.2,"backdrop_path":"/aWXG4Y6yEh80L8tqvLYToyRfWUD.jpg","original_title":"Reflections","original_language":"de"},{"id":11658,"adult":false,"title":"Tae Guk Gi: The Brotherhood of War","video":false,"overview":"When two brothers are forced to fight in the Korean War, the elder decides to take the riskiest missions if it will help shield the younger from battle.","genre_ids":[28,12,18,36,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7102,"vote_count":753,"poster_path":"/vyG8qpimh3XSlxc6OmPq8LJRJl.jpg","release_date":"2004-02-05","vote_average":7.983,"backdrop_path":"/oqaKsofz49zjNhi48sxQIq8U73X.jpg","original_title":"태극기 휘날리며","original_language":"ko"},{"id":7549,"adult":false,"title":"Fearless","video":false,"overview":"After going through a series of tragic events in his life, martial arts master Huo Yuanjia returns to Tianjin and must fight four international soldiers, in order to safeguard his nation's pride.","genre_ids":[18,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.3424,"vote_count":1371,"poster_path":"/yKJ7rjIwOa8XvACELo9eV8IvMPb.jpg","release_date":"2006-01-26","vote_average":7.509,"backdrop_path":"/6epfs9UMFbYuj4UfjHq5EDic8V9.jpg","original_title":"霍元甲","original_language":"zh"},{"id":49797,"adult":false,"title":"I Saw the Devil","video":false,"overview":"Kyung-chul is a dangerous psychopath who kills for pleasure. Soo-hyeon, a top-secret agent, decides to track down the murderer himself. He promises himself that he will do everything in his power to take vengeance against the killer, even if it means that he must become a monster himself.","genre_ids":[53,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.2253,"vote_count":2915,"poster_path":"/zp5NrmYp80axIGiEiYPmm1CW6uH.jpg","release_date":"2010-08-12","vote_average":7.791,"backdrop_path":"/ylqOWMU3nyZqg8hjJBG4EPdsGSk.jpg","original_title":"악마를 보았다","original_language":"ko"},{"id":380,"adult":false,"title":"Rain Man","video":false,"overview":"When car dealer Charlie Babbitt learns that his estranged father has died, he returns home to Cincinnati, where he discovers that he has a savant older brother named Raymond and that his father's $3 million fortune is being left to the mental institution in which Raymond lives. Motivated by his father's money, Charlie checks Raymond out of the facility in order to return with him to Los Angeles. The brothers' cross-country trip ends up changing both their lives.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.7487,"vote_count":6909,"poster_path":"/iTNHwO896WKkaoPtpMMS74d8VNi.jpg","release_date":"1988-12-12","vote_average":7.748,"backdrop_path":"/b3tos7Tsd6lsTe52Nn4TMrEQg65.jpg","original_title":"Rain Man","original_language":"en"},{"id":72190,"adult":false,"title":"World War Z","video":false,"overview":"Life for former United Nations investigator Gerry Lane and his family seems content. Suddenly, the world is plagued by a mysterious infection turning whole human populations into rampaging mindless zombies. After barely escaping the chaos, Lane is persuaded to go on a mission to investigate this disease. What follows is a perilous trek around the world where Lane must brave horrific dangers and long odds to find answers before human civilization falls.","genre_ids":[28,27,878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.9924,"vote_count":16261,"poster_path":"/aCnVdvExw6UWSeQfr0tUH3jr4qG.jpg","release_date":"2013-06-19","vote_average":6.823,"backdrop_path":"/31VpBgUX5O4Z3dn5ZbX8HLqoXH3.jpg","original_title":"World War Z","original_language":"en"},{"id":11324,"adult":false,"title":"Shutter Island","video":false,"overview":"World War II soldier-turned-U.S. Marshal Teddy Daniels investigates the disappearance of a patient from a hospital for the criminally insane, but his efforts are compromised by troubling visions and a mysterious doctor.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.0553,"vote_count":25437,"poster_path":"/nrmXQ0zcZUL8jFLrakWc90IR8z9.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-14","vote_average":8.2,"backdrop_path":"/8xt8AMb1OKC63AdhNSaYBWxB4Iq.jpg","original_title":"Shutter Island","original_language":"en"},{"id":10481,"adult":false,"title":"102 Dalmatians","video":false,"overview":"Get ready for a howling good time as an all new assortment of irresistible animal heroes are unleashed in this great family tail! In an unlikely alliance, the outrageous Waddlesworth - a parrot who thinks he's a Rottweiler - teams up with Oddball - an un-marked Dalmatian puppy eager to earn her spots! Together they embark on a laugh-packed quest to outwit the ever-scheming Cruella De Vil.","genre_ids":[10751,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0001,"vote_count":1448,"poster_path":"/ueE6u2GTECzGBtas6PFx7wwi9y0.jpg","release_date":"2000-10-07","vote_average":5.508,"backdrop_path":"/eqZ5t82asfprFcNS56eVruNT5G5.jpg","original_title":"102 Dalmatians","original_language":"en"},{"id":17689,"adult":false,"title":"The Gauntlet","video":false,"overview":"Phoenix cop Ben Shockley is well on his way to becoming a derelict when he is assigned to transport a witness from Las Vegas. The witness turns out to be a belligerent prostitute with mob ties—and incriminating information regarding a high-ranking official.","genre_ids":[18,28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3855,"vote_count":592,"poster_path":"/hYXkHixmH2W4hXA0qVJpT4ONPt1.jpg","release_date":"1977-12-17","vote_average":6.544,"backdrop_path":"/501a9Y4ighM196440ARgIXoFlh0.jpg","original_title":"The Gauntlet","original_language":"en"},{"id":264660,"adult":false,"title":"Ex Machina","video":false,"overview":"Caleb, a coder at the world's largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact with the world's first true artificial intelligence, housed in the body of a beautiful robot girl.","genre_ids":[18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.7763,"vote_count":14031,"poster_path":"/dmJW8IAKHKxFNiUnoDR7JfsK7Rp.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-21","vote_average":7.573,"backdrop_path":"/uqOuJ50EtTj7kkDIXP8LCg7G45D.jpg","original_title":"Ex Machina","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":439,"adult":false,"title":"La Dolce Vita","video":false,"overview":"Episodic journey of journalist Marcello who struggles to find his place in the world, torn between the allure of Rome's elite social scene and the stifling domesticity offered by his girlfriend, all the while searching for a way to become a serious writer.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":2.737,"vote_count":2002,"poster_path":"/2KU52apQyvyZuPsqEGMcWb4BKu2.jpg","release_date":"1960-02-05","vote_average":8.047,"backdrop_path":"/uaEfEkb2tjl4hN1oaSyzcxt4cEg.jpg","original_title":"La dolce vita","original_language":"it"},{"id":451,"adult":false,"title":"Leaving Las Vegas","video":false,"overview":"Ben Sanderson, an alcoholic Hollywood screenwriter who lost everything because of his drinking, arrives in Las Vegas to drink himself to death. There, he meets and forms an uneasy friendship and non-interference pact with prostitute Sera.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":2.4606,"vote_count":1600,"poster_path":"/wTrFpGe3U65kXTldIUxuM2hmOAK.jpg","release_date":"1995-10-27","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/uqYjy4MwB4vZScpUPGdINVaSeTd.jpg","original_title":"Leaving Las Vegas","original_language":"en"},{"id":453,"adult":false,"title":"A Beautiful Mind","video":false,"overview":"From the heights of notoriety to the depths of depravity, John Forbes Nash Jr. experiences it all. As a brilliant but socially awkward mathematician, he made a groundbreaking discovery early in his career and stands on the brink of international acclaim. But as the handsome and arrogant Nash accepts secret work in cryptography, he becomes entangled in a mysterious conspiracy. His life takes a nightmarish turn and he soon finds himself on a painful and harrowing journey of self-discovery.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":6.821,"vote_count":10876,"poster_path":"/zwzWCmH72OSC9NA0ipoqw5Zjya8.jpg","release_date":"2001-12-14","vote_average":7.854,"backdrop_path":"/vVBcIN68kFq681b4lObiNJhEVro.jpg","original_title":"A Beautiful Mind","original_language":"en"},{"id":747,"adult":false,"title":"Shaun of the Dead","video":false,"overview":"Shaun lives a supremely uneventful life, which revolves around his girlfriend, his mother, and, above all, his local pub. This gentle routine is threatened when the dead return to life and make strenuous attempts to snack on ordinary Londoners.","genre_ids":[27,35],"popularity":7.3685,"vote_count":9141,"poster_path":"/dgXPhzNJH8HFTBjXPB177yNx6RI.jpg","release_date":"2004-04-09","vote_average":7.539,"backdrop_path":"/wb34q3VgzHgL8frVMywrN3wXmqx.jpg","original_title":"Shaun of the Dead","original_language":"en"},{"id":713,"adult":false,"title":"The Piano","video":false,"overview":"When an arranged marriage brings Ada and her spirited daughter to the wilderness of nineteenth-century New Zealand, she finds herself locked in a battle of wills with both her controlling husband and a rugged frontiersman to whom she develops a forbidden attraction.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":7.0613,"vote_count":1617,"poster_path":"/dUxjG6baSzGIgP7R8BQI5rpMuET.jpg","release_date":"1993-05-18","vote_average":7.377,"backdrop_path":"/bo96LKNbkNHqWZBYBllrnjbmRBY.jpg","original_title":"The Piano","original_language":"en"},{"id":907,"adult":false,"title":"Doctor Zhivago","video":false,"overview":"The life of a Russian physician and poet who, although married to another, falls in love with a political activist's wife and experiences hardship during World War I and then the October Revolution.","genre_ids":[18,10749,10752],"popularity":3.0222,"vote_count":1246,"poster_path":"/r0Iv2BiCFYDnzc6uU1q3AJ56igT.jpg","release_date":"1965-12-22","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/y3sPNxqVBIt97EZX568OpAWBpcl.j