ll geniuses. Virtually all memory of the brilliance of the young Tenenbaums was subsequently erased by two decades of betrayal, failure, and disaster. Most of this was generally considered to be their father's fault. \"The Royal Tenenbaums\" is the story of the family's sudden, unexpected reunion one recent winter.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":4.7095,"vote_count":4883,"poster_path":"/nG7hZJn7wQTSDCQT39Gy3s3tbrp.jpg","release_date":"2001-10-05","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/cbuX448RKetr5Y5cZkmJEfu3xji.jpg","original_title":"The Royal Tenenbaums","original_language":"en"},{"id":1258312,"adult":false,"title":"An Affair to Remember!","video":false,"overview":"A wife reveals to her younger husband that she is having an affair.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":0.2957,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/wNN0CsuWoxKQJfDmLuOuprDtjhT.jpg","release_date":"2023-11-25","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/atcZkidLIJycEPxx9K3vclAHLbR.jpg","original_title":"En affär att minnas!","original_language":"sv"},{"id":9707,"adult":false,"title":"Bubba Ho-tep","video":false,"overview":"Bubba Ho-tep tells the \"true\" story of what really became of Elvis Presley. We find Elvis as an elderly resident in an East Texas rest home, who switched identities with an Elvis impersonator years before his \"death,\" then missed his chance to switch back. He must team up with JFK and fight an ancient Egyptian mummy for the souls of their fellow residents.","genre_ids":[35,27,53,9648,14],"popularity":2.6766,"vote_count":684,"poster_path":"/pKQBit5ZV7GEOTiMBSYC6xBn86K.jpg","release_date":"2002-06-09","vote_average":6.487,"backdrop_path":"/1TpUjiwMYtASIJYbtuyPkCe4kKw.jpg","original_title":"Bubba Ho-tep","original_language":"en"},{"id":1259102,"adult":false,"title":"Eternity","video":false,"overview":"In an afterlife where souls have one week to decide where to spend eternity, Joan is faced with the impossible choice between the man she spent her life with and her first love, who died young and 